This is a git repo

library to install:
sudo apt-get install librxtx-java

to execute:
java -jar target/restprj-1.0-SNAPSHOT.jar

to enable/disable debug:
touch /tmp/hal9000debug
rm /tmp/hal9000debug

to browse:
GET:
http://localhost:8080/hal9000/clock
http://localhost:8080/hal9000/thermo

POST:
http://localhost:8080/hal9000/debug?enable=true
http://localhost:8080/hal9000/setclock
http://localhost:8080/hal9000/thermo?required=<Celsius*10>
http://localhost:8080/hal9000/thermo?hysteresis=<Celsius*10>
